The paper discusses a method used in different domains for responding to changing conditions, which suggests a focus on software engineering (cs.SE) and cybernetics (cs.CY). The paper also mentions monitoring systems' customization and re-composition, which could fall under systems and control (cs.SY) and cryptography and security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper uses data mining techniques, which could be related to distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
